import React from 'react' import {useState, useEffect} from 'react' import useAxios from "../utils/useAxios" import {jwtDecode as jwt_decode} from 'jwt-decode' function Dashboard() { const [res, setRes] = useState("") const api = useAxios(); const token = localStorage.getItem("authTokens") if (token){ const decode = jwtDecode(token) var user_id = decode.user_id var username = decode.username var full_name = decode.full_name var image = decode.image } useEffect(() => { const fetchData = async () => { try{ const response = await api.get("/test/") setRes(response.data.response) } catch (error) { console.log(error); setRes("Something went wrong") } } fetchData() }, []) useEffect(() => { const fetchPostData = async () => { try{ const response = await api.post("/test/") setRes(response.data.response) } catch (error) { console.log(error); setRes("Something went wrong") } } fetchPostData() }, []) return (
